            <p class="text-neutral-dark-gray leading-relaxed">From structural framing to finish carpentry, we craft durable spaces tuned to how you live.</p>
            <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-neutral-dark-gray">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"></span>Full builds, ADUs, and expansions</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"></span>Envelope upgrades for efficiency</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-md hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg transition">
