              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"></span>Roofing, siding, and waterproofing</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-3xl bg-neutral-dark text-neutral-white p-8 lg:p-10 shadow-2xl flex flex-col justify-between">
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-accent">Why teams pick us</p>
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold leading-tight">One partner from permit to punch list.</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-light-gray leading-relaxed">
              Dedicated site leads, vetted trades, and a reporting cadence that keeps stakeholders aligned‚Äîso projects stay predictable.
            </p>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
              <div class="bg-white/10 rounded-2xl p-4 border border-white/10">
                <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-accent">48 hrs</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-neutral-light-gray">Average bid turnaround</p>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-white/10 rounded-2xl p-4 border border-white/10">
                <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-white">3</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-neutral-light-gray">Dedicated supervisors per job</p>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-white/10 rounded-2xl p-4 border border-white/10">
