              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-neutral-dark">Licensed specialists on every site</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-neutral-dark-gray">Structural, electrical, and finish teams aligned from day one.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3 bg-white/80 border border-neutral-200 rounded-2xl px-4 py-4 shadow-sm">
              <span class="mt-1 h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-accent"></span>
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-neutral-dark">Transparent budgeting & reporting</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-neutral-dark-gray">Milestone check-ins with cost tracking you can actually read.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3 bg-white/80 border border-neutral-200 rounded-2xl px-4 py-4 shadow-sm">
